user.biography: We’re your Ultimate Sports Lodge. It’s where you come to watch every game in HD, the beer is an icy 29° and the food leaves you coming back for more.

node.text: Tonight: UFC 265 is going down! The man with 20 knockouts, Derrick Lewis, takes on undefeated Ciryl Gane in the Heavyweight Interim Title Bout. Get here for every second of knockout action! Contact your favorite location for availability and cover info. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #UFC265 #UFC

node.text: Bring your league to Twin Peaks this year for the ultimate Fantasy Football drafting experience! We have sweet deals for the whole team. Book your spot now at https://twinpeaksrestaurant.com/fantasydraft

node.text: When's the last time you had something REALLY good to eat? Get to Twin Peaks and score the Mom's Pot Roast. It’s slow cooked with brown gravy and served with garlic mashed potatoes and green beans, making for the perfect match. Come get you some! #Yum #PotRoast #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant
